                            <td class="py-4 px-6">Year 3</td>
                            <td class="py-4 px-6 text-myGreen font-medium">+10%</td>
                            <td class="py-4 px-6">(\$646,250) - \$50,000 = <strong class="text-myRed">\$596,250</strong></td>
                        </tr>
                    </tbody>
                </table>
            </div>
            <p class="text-xl text-gray-800 leading-relaxed my-6">
                After 3 years, Retiree A has lost nearly <strong>40%</strong> of their money. They are in a death spiral and will likely go broke.
            </p>

